lead_paragraph: Lara Arruabarrena of Spain beat Monica Niculescu of Romania 6-0, 2-6, 6-0 on Sunday to win the Korea Open and claim her second WTA singles title.

headline.print_headline: Arruabarrena Beats Niculescu in 3 Sets to Win Korea Open
